      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["# Fish Audio S2\n\nUse `[Character]` for suite character switching. Fish's official inline instructions remain written as `<instruction>` in the suite and are converted internally at the engine boundary.\n\nSpeaker 1 is the narrator input. Connect additional Character Voices nodes to Speaker 2 and Speaker 3. Native Multi-Speaker keeps turns in one Fish request; Custom Character Switching generates each segment independently."]
